Unfortunately non of the programs have really useful helpfiles...

Few essential points:

* When using "siglscope" click to graph axis and zoom in/out with mouse wheel.

* Command without output:
* ./usbtmc_command --device=/dev/usbtmc0 --command ARM

* Query with output:
* ./usbtmc_command --device=/dev/usbtmc0 '*IDN?'

* Download wave:
* ./accwave_siglentsds1000 --device=/dev/usbtmc0 --channel=1 > wave.csv

* Download wave and calculate spectrum:
* ./accspectrum_siglentsds1000 --device=/dev/usbtmc0 --channel=1 > spectrum.csv

